12
00:02:15,836 --> 00:02:17,203
HUH?

13
00:02:17,303 --> 00:02:18,338
[SHIROE] LATER.

14
00:02:18,438 --> 00:02:19,840
[NAOTSUGU]
HEY. WHAT IS IT?

15
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:21,407
[SHIROE] MARIELLE'S GONNA
DO WHAT SHE CAN TO GET

16
00:02:21,508 --> 00:02:23,810
IN TOUCH WITH SERARA
AND GET BACK TO US ON IT.

17
00:02:23,910 --> 00:02:25,178
WORKS FOR ME.

18
00:02:25,278 --> 00:02:26,713
