AKIHABARA CATHEDRAL.

23
00:02:39,425 --> 00:02:43,997
BUT SHE WOULD REVIVE
AT THE SUSUKINO CATHEDRAL.

24
00:02:44,097 --> 00:02:45,431
[AKATSUKI]
I UNDERSTAND.

25
00:02:45,532 --> 00:02:48,334
[NAOTSUGU] AND THE PROBLEM
IS SHE'S ON A BRIGANDIA

26
00:02:48,434 --> 00:02:51,071
GUY'S FRIEND LIST, RIGHT?

27
00:02:51,171 --> 00:02:52,639
[SHIROE] YEAH.

28
00:02:52,739 --> 00:02:55,308
[SHIROE] SHE'S MANAGED TO FIND
A PRIVATE ZONE TO HIDE IN

29
00:02:55,408 --> 00:02:57,878
SO THEY CAN'T FIND HER,

30
00:02:57,978 --> 00:02:59,479
BUT THE SECOND SHE GOES OUT,

31
00:02:59,580 --> 00:03:02,849
WHOEVER THAT GUY IS CAN USE HIS
HUD TO FIND WHEREVER SHE GOES.

32
00:03:02,949 --> 00:03:05,519
[NAOTSUGU] SO WHEN IT'S
TIME FOR HER, SHE HAS
TO KEEP ON RUNNING.

33
00:03:05,619 --> 00:03:07,420
[SHIROE] AKATSUKI, I'D LIKE
YOU TO KEEP YOURSELF HIDDEN

34
00:03:07,521 --> 00:03:10,023
WITH SNEAK AND SILENT MOVE
IF YOU WOULD, PLEASE.

35
00:03:10,123 --> 00:03:11,592
[AKATUSKI] YOU DON'T
HAVE TO SAY, "PLEASE."

36
00:03:11,692 --> 00:03:12,893
[SHIROE] UH.

37
00:03:14,094 --> 00:03:15,428
HEH.

38
00:03:15,529 --> 00:03:17,731
