ENABLES SELF‐CONCEALMENT,

39
00:03:17,831 --> 00:03:21,201
WHILE SILENT MOVE ALLOWS
MOTION WITHOUT ANY SOUND.

40
00:03:21,301 --> 00:03:23,804
THEY'RE TRACKER CLASS SKILLS.

41
00:03:23,904 --> 00:03:27,774
[NAOTSUGU] ALL RIGHT!
LET'S LAY THE SMACKDOWN
ON THESE DUMMIES!

42
00:03:34,014 --> 00:03:35,882
[BEEPING]

43
00:03:35,982 --> 00:03:40,621
HA. WHEREVER YOU'RE HIDING,
LITTLE GIRL, I'LL FIND YOU.

44
00:03:40,721 --> 00:03:43,757
