ALL RIGHT. WE'RE HERE.

60
00:04:22,095 --> 00:04:23,997
STAND WATCH, AKATSUKI.

61
00:04:24,097 --> 00:04:25,231
[AKATSUKI] WILL DO.

62
00:04:25,331 --> 00:04:27,233
[SHIROE]
NAOTSUGU, HANG OUT HERE.

63
00:04:27,333 --> 00:04:29,269
[NAOTSUGU] ROGER.

64
00:04:33,239 --> 00:04:36,276
[SERARA]
UH, HMM. HMM.

65
00:04:37,277 --> 00:04:39,513
I'M SERARA OF CRESCENT
MOON ALLIANCE.

66
