UH, I SHOULD THANK YOU
FOR COMING FOR ME.

67
00:04:44,885 --> 00:04:46,587
HUH?

68
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,655
MEOW.

69
00:04:50,356 --> 00:04:53,159
HEY. IS THAT
REALLY YOU, CHIEF?!

70
00:04:53,259 --> 00:04:54,795
[NYAN‐TA] MMMYEAH.

71
00:04:54,895 --> 00:04:55,729
UH!

72
00:04:55,829 --> 00:04:56,863
[NYAN‐TA] WELL NOW,

73
00:04:56,963 --> 00:05:00,534
