76
00:05:05,405 --> 00:05:07,307
UM, I, UH...

77
00:05:07,407 --> 00:05:09,275
[SHIROE] YEAH, IT DOES.

78
00:05:09,375 --> 00:05:11,277
I SHOULD INTRODUCE MYSELF.

79
00:05:11,377 --> 00:05:12,913
I'M SHIROE. IT'S NICE
TO MEET YOU.

80
00:05:13,013 --> 00:05:15,749
