REALLY KNOW EACH OTHER?

89
00:05:36,336 --> 00:05:38,639
MMM, SOMETHING LIKE
THAT, BABY. HEH HEH HEH.

90
00:05:38,739 --> 00:05:42,175
SHIROECHI USED TO CHECK
ME DILIGENTLY FOR FLEAS.

91
00:05:42,275 --> 00:05:44,645
[SHIROE] I MOST
CERTAINLY DID NOT!

92
00:05:45,411 --> 00:05:47,781
