90 ASSASSIN.

97
00:05:59,059 --> 00:06:00,460
SHE'S SCARY GOOD.

98
00:06:00,561 --> 00:06:03,730
SO YOU BROUGHT
NAOTSUGUCCHI, DID YOU?

99
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,799
[NYAN‐TA]
AND A NEW FRIEND, TOO?

100
00:06:05,899 --> 00:06:07,300
MEOW.

101
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:08,635
