A MONK, BUT...

118
00:06:44,971 --> 00:06:48,374
[SHIROE] HUH? A BEAR
CARVED OUT OF WOOD?

119
00:06:48,474 --> 00:06:50,376
[NYAN‐TA] THAT'S
BRIGANDIA'S LEADER,

120
00:06:50,476 --> 00:06:52,412
GUILD MASTER DEMICAS.

121
00:06:52,513 --> 00:06:53,814
[SERARA] HUH?

122
00:06:54,214 --> 00:06:56,182
(WHIMPERS)

123
00:06:56,917 --> 00:06:58,051
(CHIME)

124
00:06:58,151 --> 00:06:59,285
NAOTSUGU.

125
00:06:59,385 --> 00:07:01,121
I'M HERE, MAN.

126
00:07:01,221 --> 00:07:03,524
