HANDLE THIS, AND YOU'RE
GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.

169
00:08:42,589 --> 00:08:45,526
[SERARA]
YEAH, BUT, NYAN‐TA...

170
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:52,098
