FOR YOU, LITTLE SERARA.

171
00:08:52,198 --> 00:08:53,967
HA HA HA!

172
00:08:56,369 --> 00:08:59,873
(WHIMPERING)

173
00:09:00,406 --> 00:09:02,509
HEH.

174
00:09:02,609 --> 00:09:03,476
[SHIROE]
CHIEF NYAN‐TA.

175
00:09:03,577 --> 00:09:04,945
[NYAN‐TA]
TALK TO ME.

176
00:09:05,045 --> 00:09:07,514
