A SERIOUS QUESTION?

178
00:09:10,083 --> 00:09:11,585
HMM.

179
00:09:13,319 --> 00:09:14,721
[NYAN‐TA]
DON'T WORRY.

180
00:09:14,821 --> 00:09:17,423
NONE OF THESE
KNUCKLEHEAD FOOLS
IS GONNA LAY A HAND

181
00:09:17,524 --> 00:09:19,926
ON YOU, LITTLE LADY.

182
00:09:20,026 --> 00:09:22,462
OK. SO WHICH ONE OF
YOU FUTURE DEAD GUYS IS

183
00:09:22,563 --> 00:09:24,297
