[DEMICAS] HA! LONG TIME,
NO SEE, LITTLE LADY.

194
00:09:50,557 --> 00:09:52,125
(WHIMPERING)

195
00:09:52,225 --> 00:09:53,927
[DEMICAS] YOU DIDN'T
REALLY THINK I
WAS JUST GONNA

