222
00:10:51,985 --> 00:10:53,954
LITTLE BATHROBE
AND EVERYTHING.

223
00:10:54,054 --> 00:10:56,489
YOU LOOK MORE SERIOUS
THAN YOUR BOSS DOES.

224
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:58,024
IN CASE YOU
HAVEN'T HEARD OF ME,

225
00:10:58,124 --> 00:11:00,861
I AM CALLED LONDARK
OF THE GRAY STEEL.

226
00:11:00,961 --> 00:11:02,696
[SHIROE] OH. THAT'S QUITE
THE FANCY NICKNAME.

227
00:11:02,796 --> 00:11:04,898
NOT TOO BAD, I SUPPOSE.

228
00:11:04,998 --> 00:11:06,900
I THINK IT WOULD PROPERLY
SETTLE THE SCORE HERE IF

229
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:09,803
ONLY OUR STRONGEST
FIGHTERS DID BATTLE.

230
00:11:10,737 --> 00:11:13,907
CHIEF NYAN‐TA WILL
FIGHT YOU, GRAY STEEL.

231
00:11:14,007 --> 00:11:16,209
MYSELF AND THE ELF
CAN FINISH THIS.

232
00:11:16,309 --> 00:11:21,982
SINCE THE MEATHEAD HERE
IS TOO AFRAID TO FIGHT
ALL ALONE, THAT'LL WORK.

233
00:11:22,448 --> 00:11:23,717
OK. FINE.

234
00:11:23,817 --> 00:11:26,520
YOU WANT TO GET
CRUSHED, DON'T YOU?

235
00:11:26,620 --> 00:11:27,988
DON'T YOU?!

236
00:11:28,755 --> 00:11:31,224
HUH! AAH!

237
00:11:33,126 --> 00:11:34,460
AAH!

238
00:11:38,264 --> 00:11:39,365
HEH.

239
00:11:40,701 --> 00:11:42,335
VERY GOOD.

240
00:11:44,605 --> 00:11:47,140
YOU READY TO GET
ALL SCRATCHED UP?

241
00:11:55,248 --> 00:11:56,883
MR. CAT!

242
00:11:58,018 --> 00:11:59,553
[NYAN‐TA]
IF IT'S ALL THE
SAME TO YOU,

243
00:11:59,653 --> 00:12:03,624
I'D RATHER NOT HAVE THE LADY
WITNESS TOO MUCH BLOOD.

244
00:12:03,724 --> 00:12:05,291
JUST LET ME KNOW IF
YOU WANT ME TO TAKE IT

245
00:12:05,391 --> 00:12:06,627
EASY ON YOU.

246
00:12:06,727 --> 00:12:08,762
YEAH. KEEP TALKING, CAT.

247
00:12:08,862 --> 00:12:10,964
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
DEMICAS IS IN THE MONK CLASS,

248
00:12:11,064 --> 00:12:16,169
1 OF THE 3 WARRIOR CLASSES,
SIMILAR TO GUARDIAN AND SAMURAI.

249
00:12:17,237 --> 00:12:19,472
YAAH!

250
00:12:20,974 --> 00:12:22,643
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
IN THE WORLD OF "ELDER TALES,"

251
00:12:22,743 --> 00:12:26,913
VARIOUS SKILLS AND
ATTACKS HAVE ACTIVATION
PERIODS CALLED CAST TIMES.

252
00:12:27,013 --> 00:12:31,317
THEY ALSO HAVE COOLDOWN
TIMES CALLED RECAST TIMES.

253
00:12:32,185 --> 00:12:33,654
[DEMICAS] UGH!

254
00:12:33,754 --> 00:12:36,189
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
CAST TIME IS THE AMOUNT OF
TIME IT TAKES A SPELL TO

255
00:12:36,289 --> 00:12:39,993
HAVE ITS FULL EFFECT
ONCE IT'S BEEN CAST.

256
00:12:41,027 --> 00:12:42,863
COOLDOWN TIME IS THE
AMOUNT OF TIME IT TAKES

257
00:12:42,963 --> 00:12:46,933
BEFORE YOU CAN REUSE A
SPELL AFTER IT'S BEEN CAST.

258
00:12:48,835 --> 00:12:51,738
[DEMICAS] AURA SABER!

259
00:12:51,838 --> 00:12:53,373
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
MONKS HAVE SHORT COOLDOWNS.

260
00:12:53,473 --> 00:12:55,842
THIS ALLOWS THEM TO
CREATE CHAINS OF ATTACKS,

261
00:12:55,942 --> 00:12:58,478
GIVING THEIR OPPONENT
LITTLE ROOM TO RECOVER.

262
00:12:58,579 --> 00:13:00,480
[DEMICAS] RAAH!

263
00:13:00,581 --> 00:13:02,583
PHANTOM STEP!

264
00:13:02,683 --> 00:13:03,950
HA HA!

265
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:05,886
LEAVE IT TO A CAT TO THINK
HE'S GONNA BEAT ME BY

266
00:13:05,986 --> 00:13:08,955
SCRATCHING ME
WITH TOY SWORDS!

267
00:13:09,055 --> 00:13:10,156
[NYAN‐TA]
CHECK YOURSELF.

268
00:13:10,256 --> 00:13:13,894
A RAPIER IS A
GENTLEMAN'S WEAPON.

269
00:13:13,994 --> 00:13:17,564
[SERARA] OHH! NYAN‐TA IS
RUNNING LOW ON HIT POINTS.

270
00:13:17,664 --> 00:13:20,734
IT LOOKS LIKE OUR
GUILD MASTER HAS
THIS ONE SEWN UP.

271
00:13:20,834 --> 00:13:22,468
UNLESS...

272
00:13:22,569 --> 00:13:23,837
[DEMICAS] RAAH!

273
00:13:23,937 --> 00:13:24,938
[NYAN‐TA] HA!

274
00:13:25,038 --> 00:13:27,240
(DEMICAS GRUNTING)

275
00:13:27,340 --> 00:13:28,542
[NYAN‐TA] HEH HEH.

276
00:13:28,642 --> 00:13:30,544
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER] THE PIRATE
SWORDSMAN, SWASHBUCKLER.

277
00:13:30,644 --> 00:13:32,045
(DEMICAS GRUNTING)

278
00:13:32,145 --> 00:13:34,615
IT'S ONE OF THE SPECIALIZED
WEAPON CLASSES AND ONE

279
00:13:34,715 --> 00:13:37,250
OF THE FEW THAT
CAN DUAL WIELD.

280
00:13:38,451 --> 00:13:40,954
WHAT MAKES IT TRULY UNIQUE,
THOUGH, IS THE FACT THAT IT

281
00:13:41,054 --> 00:13:44,057
LOWERS THE TARGET'S
ABILITIES WITH EACH STRIKE.

282
00:13:44,157 --> 00:13:47,393
LOWERED ATTACK, LOWERED DODGE,
LOWERED DEFENSE...

283
00:13:47,493 --> 00:13:51,197
BIT BY BIT UNTIL AN
OPPONENT JUST CAN'T FIGHT.

284
00:13:51,297 --> 00:13:52,799
[LONDARK] HE'S ABOUT
TO SUFFER A DEATH

285
00:13:52,899 --> 00:13:54,768
OF A THOUSAND TINY CUTS.

286
00:13:54,868 --> 00:13:56,837
WHOA! NOT GOOD!

287
00:13:56,937 --> 00:14:00,306
[LONDARK, THINKING]
IT WOULD APPEAR AS
THOUGH DEMICAS IS LOSING.

288
00:14:00,406 --> 00:14:03,176
[DEMICAS]
COME ON!
FIGHT LIKE A MAN!

289
00:14:03,276 --> 00:14:05,311
YOU GOT TO HAVE MORE
FIGHT IN YOU THAN THAT!

290
00:14:05,411 --> 00:14:07,581
[NYAN‐TA] HEH HEH.
COMING FROM YOU, THE WORDS

291
00:14:07,681 --> 00:14:10,817
"FIGHT LIKE A MAN"
HAVE TO BE THE MOST
RIDICULOUS THING

292
00:14:10,917 --> 00:14:12,418
I'VE EVER HEARD.

293
00:14:12,519 --> 00:14:13,486
HUH?

294
00:14:13,587 --> 00:14:14,955
[SHIROE] SERARA.
[SERARA] HUH?

295
00:14:15,055 --> 00:14:16,923
[SHIROE]
WHEN I GIVE THE SIGNAL,
I WANT YOU TO CAST

296
00:14:17,023 --> 00:14:18,725
A HEALING PULSE
ON EVERYONE.

297
00:14:18,825 --> 00:14:20,026
[SERARA] HUH?

298
00:14:20,126 --> 00:14:21,762
[SERARA] EVERYONE?

299
00:14:21,862 --> 00:14:23,664
I'M DONE PLAYING
WITH YOU, MAN.

300
00:14:23,764 --> 00:14:25,966
MAGIC USERS,
CAST HEALING ON ME!

301
00:14:26,066 --> 00:14:29,603
THE REST OF YOU, JUMP THIS
CAT'S ASS AND KILL HIM NOW!

302
00:14:29,703 --> 00:14:31,337
[MAN 1] AH...
[MAN 2] UH...

303
00:14:31,437 --> 00:14:32,472
DO IT.

304
00:14:32,573 --> 00:14:33,740
OH, RIGHT.

305
00:14:33,840 --> 00:14:36,577
(SHOUTING)

306
00:14:37,010 --> 00:14:42,482
ANCHOR HOWL!

307
00:14:42,583 --> 00:14:44,885
(GROANING)

308
00:14:44,985 --> 00:14:47,353
[DEMICAS] YOU'RE
PLAYING DIRTY, TANK BOY!

309
00:14:47,453 --> 00:14:48,188
NOT BAD!

310
00:14:48,288 --> 00:14:49,890
HEALER TEAMS,
HEAL DEMICAS!

311
00:14:49,990 --> 00:14:51,658
[HEALERS] YEAH!

312
00:14:52,626 --> 00:14:55,028
[DEMICAS] GAH! HYAH!

313
00:14:57,998 --> 00:14:59,199
HEH HEH.

314
00:14:59,299 --> 00:15:00,967
[LONDARK] FIGHTERS,
CONCENTRATE YOUR ATTACKS

315
00:15:01,067 --> 00:15:02,736
ON THE GUARDIAN!

316
00:15:02,836 --> 00:15:05,606
(FIGHTERS SHOUTING)

317
00:15:05,706 --> 00:15:07,140
HE'S GONNA DIE!

318
00:15:07,240 --> 00:15:09,976
[SHIROE] CAST YOUR
HEALING SPELL NOW.

319
00:15:10,076 --> 00:15:12,546
HUH? RIGHT.

320
00:15:13,880 --> 00:15:17,383
HEARTBEAT HEALING!

321
00:15:19,553 --> 00:15:24,057
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
DRUID IS ONE OF THE
HEALING CLASSES.

322
00:15:25,258 --> 00:15:27,427
ONCE THEY CAST A HEALING
PULSE ON SOMEONE,

323
00:15:27,528 --> 00:15:30,496
IT REMAINS IN EFFECT
FOR A SHORT TIME.

324
00:15:31,364 --> 00:15:33,534
[SERARA] IT'S NOT
GOING FAST ENOUGH.

325
00:15:33,634 --> 00:15:35,168
I CAN'T DO ANYMORE!

326
00:15:35,268 --> 00:15:37,137
I'M NOT STRONG ENOUGH!

327
00:15:37,237 --> 00:15:39,172
[SHIROE] NAOTSUGU'S
GONNA BE FINE.

328
00:15:39,272 --> 00:15:41,942
SEND THE REST OF YOUR
SPELL OVER TO NYAN‐TA.

329
00:15:42,042 --> 00:15:45,245
[SERARA] OK, BUT THEY'RE
BOTH IN DANGER, AREN'T THEY?

330
00:15:45,345 --> 00:15:47,848
IF YOU CAN'T HELP
THEM BOTH, THEN DON'T.

331
00:15:47,948 --> 00:15:49,716
FOCUS ON WHAT YOU CAN.

332
00:15:49,816 --> 00:15:51,552
IT'LL HELP.

333
00:15:59,425 --> 00:16:01,628
HEAL!

334
00:16:03,163 --> 00:16:04,631
[DEMICAS] HA HA HA!

335
00:16:04,731 --> 00:16:06,967
WHATEVER! HYAH!

336
00:16:07,433 --> 00:16:08,702
UNH!

337
00:16:11,104 --> 00:16:16,342
[DEMICAS] IT MUST BE HARD
TO GET BY WITH ONE CRAPPY
HEALER, PUSSYCAT.

338
00:16:16,442 --> 00:16:19,680
YOUR WHOLE TEAM OF HEALERS
CAN'T FIX YOUR HAIR.

339
00:16:19,780 --> 00:16:21,715
[DEMICAS]
AW, SHUT UP!

340
00:16:21,815 --> 00:16:25,018
[DEMICAS] LOOKS LIKE
YOUR WARRIOR BUDDY'S
ABOUT TO GET CREAMED.

341
00:16:25,118 --> 00:16:27,287
HA HA HA!

342
00:16:27,387 --> 00:16:29,590
[NAOTSUGU] SHIROE!
[SERARA] HUH?

343
00:16:29,690 --> 00:16:31,091
HEH.

344
00:16:32,993 --> 00:16:34,861
GET READY TO CAST IT.

345
00:16:34,961 --> 00:16:36,496
[SERARA] UH! RIGHT.

346
00:16:38,732 --> 00:16:41,301
CASTLE OF STONE!

347
00:16:42,869 --> 00:16:45,171
(FIGHTERS SHOUTING)

348
00:16:45,972 --> 00:16:47,974
(FIGHTERS GROAN)

349
00:16:48,074 --> 00:16:50,243
[FIGHTER] WE DIDN'T
EVEN HURT HIM!

350
00:16:50,343 --> 00:16:52,178
[SHIROE, VOICE‐OVER]
CASTLE OF STONE.

351
00:16:52,278 --> 00:16:54,915
THIS SPELL BLOCKS ALL
DAMAGE FROM ALL OPPONENTS

352
00:16:55,015 --> 00:16:56,917
FOR A 10‐SECOND
PERIOD OF TIME.

353
00:16:57,017 --> 00:17:00,887
IT'S AN EMERGENCY DEFENSE THAT'S
ONLY AVAILABLE TO GUARDIANS.

354
00:17:00,987 --> 00:17:01,855
HUH!

355
00:17:01,955 --> 00:17:03,123
[SHIROE] OK NOW.

356
00:17:03,223 --> 00:17:05,425
CAST ALL YOUR HEALING
SPELLS ON NAOTSUGU!

357
00:17:05,526 --> 00:17:06,627
OK.

358
00:17:07,193 --> 00:17:10,597
HEALING WIND!

359
00:17:11,998 --> 00:17:15,235
[DEMICAS]
YOU BETTER STOP WASTING
OUR TIME, LITTLE GIRL!

360
00:17:15,335 --> 00:17:18,438
THAT CASTLE OF STONE HAS A
10‐MINUTE COOLDOWN PERIOD.

361
00:17:18,539 --> 00:17:20,406
IF HE JUST USED IT A
DEFENSIVE SKILL HE CAN'T

362
00:17:20,507 --> 00:17:23,043
USE AGAIN FOR ANOTHER
10 MINUTES OR SO,

363
00:17:23,143 --> 00:17:24,410
HE'S IN BAD SHAPE.

364
00:17:24,511 --> 00:17:26,146
HE MUST BE STARTING TO
PANIC OR AT LEAST RUNNING

365
00:17:26,246 --> 00:17:28,048
OUT OF OPTIONS IF HE
CAN'T COME UP WITH BETTER

366
00:17:28,148 --> 00:17:29,449
DEFENSES THAN THAT.

367
00:17:29,550 --> 00:17:31,184
[DEMICAS] WHEN THAT
SPELL RUNS OUT,

368
00:17:31,284 --> 00:17:33,386
YOU'RE A DEAD MAN!

369
00:17:33,486 --> 00:17:36,089
I'M GONNA ENJOY
PUNISHING YOU FOR THIS.

370
00:17:36,189 --> 00:17:39,259
COUNT ON IT.

371
00:17:39,359 --> 00:17:43,063
COME ON. YOU'VE GOT TO GET
HEALTHY FASTER THAN THAT!

372
00:17:43,163 --> 00:17:46,466
TIGER ECHO FIST!

373
00:17:48,034 --> 00:17:51,171
[SERARA]
MASTER NYAN‐TA!

374
00:17:51,271 --> 00:17:54,074
[NYAN‐TA] IT'S ABOUT TIME
TO TAKE CARE OF BUSINESS.

375
00:17:54,174 --> 00:17:56,142
READY, SHIROECHI?

376
00:17:56,242 --> 00:17:59,179
ABSOLUTELY. READY WHEN
YOU ARE, CHIEF.

377
00:17:59,279 --> 00:18:02,182
[DEMICAS] YOU FINALLY
READY TO DIE, PUNK?!

378
00:18:02,282 --> 00:18:04,818
[SHIROE]
THORN BIND HOSTAGE!

379
00:18:06,653 --> 00:18:07,821
(GRUNTING)

380
00:18:07,921 --> 00:18:08,955
[DEMICAS]
FREAKING PLANTS!

381
00:18:09,055 --> 00:18:10,223
ARE YOU KIDDING?!

382
00:18:10,323 --> 00:18:12,559
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO
DO BETTER THAN THAT!

383
00:18:12,659 --> 00:18:13,894
UH! HA!

384
00:18:13,994 --> 00:18:15,696
COME HERE!

385
00:18:15,796 --> 00:18:17,263
YAHH!

386
00:18:27,173 --> 00:18:28,675
[DEMICAS] UH...

387
00:18:31,077 --> 00:18:34,247
AAH!

388
00:18:38,785 --> 00:18:40,721
WHA‐? IMPOSSIBLE.

389
00:18:40,821 --> 00:18:43,323
OUR GUILD MASTER.

390
00:18:43,423 --> 00:18:46,126
[LONDARK] THAT ATTACK TOOK
ALL OF HIS HIT POINTS.

391
00:18:46,226 --> 00:18:48,595
HOW DID YOU DO THAT?

392
00:18:53,166 --> 00:18:55,268
HEALING TEAM, RECAST NOW!

393
00:18:55,368 --> 00:18:58,539
WE STILL HAVE
A CHANCE TO‐ AH!

394
00:18:59,105 --> 00:19:01,374
OH, CRAP.

395
00:19:04,177 --> 00:19:06,046
[COINS SCATTERING]

396
00:19:06,146 --> 00:19:08,782
[AKATSUKI, VOICE‐OVER]
THERE IS NO SINGLE ATTACK
FROM A SWASHBUCKLER

397
00:19:08,882 --> 00:19:13,186
THAT COULD EVER HOPE TO
DEFEAT A LEVEL 90 MONK.

398
00:19:13,286 --> 00:19:15,255
EVEN AN ASSASSIN LIKE
MYSELF WITH THE HIGHEST

399
00:19:15,355 --> 00:19:18,191
ATTACK POWER AMONG WEAPON
SPECIALIZATION CLASSES

400
00:19:18,291 --> 00:19:20,493
CAN'T ACCOMPLISH THAT.

401
00:19:20,594 --> 00:19:25,198
MORE THAN LIKELY,
THE SECRET LIES IN
MY LORD'S SPELL,

402
00:19:25,298 --> 00:19:27,433
THORN BIND HOSTAGE.

403
00:19:27,534 --> 00:19:29,469
EVERY SUCCESSFUL HIT BY
SOMEONE IN YOUR PARTY

404
00:19:29,570 --> 00:19:33,740
CAUSES 1,000 HIT POINTS
DAMAGE TO THE PLAYER
BOUND BY THE SPELL.

405
00:19:33,840 --> 00:19:37,177
SLASHING ALL 5 THORNS
DOES 5,000 DAMAGE.

406
00:19:37,277 --> 00:19:40,346
STILL, DEMICAS HAD MORE
THAN 5,000 HIT POINTS

407
00:19:40,446 --> 00:19:42,916
LEFT AND HAD HEALED
SOME PRIOR DAMAGE.

408
00:19:43,016 --> 00:19:46,186
SO MY LORD KNEW THAT HE
WOULD BE ABLE TO RECAST
HIS THORN BIND HOSTAGE

409
00:19:46,286 --> 00:19:49,723
WITHIN THE NEXT 15 SECONDS.

410
00:19:49,823 --> 00:19:52,125
THE SWASHBUCKLER WAITED
14 SECONDS TO BEGIN

411
00:19:52,225 --> 00:19:53,827
HIS ATTACK.

412
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:56,096
HE SCORED 9 HITS.

413
00:19:56,196 --> 00:19:58,632
HIS FIRST 5 HITS CAME QUICKLY.

414
00:20:01,134 --> 00:20:04,671
EACH SLASH WOULD
TAKE . 22 SECONDS.

415
00:20:06,206 --> 00:20:08,642
AND AFTER HE SLASHED
THE FIFTH THORN,

416
00:20:08,742 --> 00:20:11,878
MY LORD MUST HAVE
RECAST THE SPELL.

417
00:20:12,979 --> 00:20:16,182
AND THEN HE CUT 4 MORE.

418
00:20:16,282 --> 00:20:18,284
I DIDN'T SEE IT CLEARLY,
BUT IT EXPLAINS

419
00:20:18,384 --> 00:20:22,255
THE 5,000 DAMAGE FOR EACH
THORN IN THE FIRST CAST,

420
00:20:22,355 --> 00:20:24,257
THE ADDITIONAL 5,000
WHEN THEY WERE ALL CUT,

421
00:20:24,357 --> 00:20:26,660
AND NOW 4,000 MORE PLUS
THE ONE THORN STILL ON HIS

422
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:30,396
BODY, 14,000 HIT POINTS
IN ONE ATTACK.

423
00:20:30,496 --> 00:20:33,366
THAT HAD TO BE WHY NAOTSUGU
USED CASTLE OF STONE.

424
00:20:33,466 --> 00:20:35,736
HE MUST HAVE KNOWN THEY
WERE GOING TO DO IT,

425
00:20:35,836 --> 00:20:39,205
BUT THEY DIDN'T EVEN
COORDINATE AHEAD OF TIME.

426
00:20:39,305 --> 00:20:44,511
[AKATSUKI, THINKING] INCREDIBLE.
I DON'T KNOW IF I COULD DO THAT.

427
00:20:44,611 --> 00:20:47,180
[NAOTSUGU] YOU BETTER DROP
THOSE SWORDS, PUNKS!

428
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:49,550
(GROANS)

429
00:20:49,650 --> 00:20:51,351
[SHIROE] WE CAME THROUGH
THE DEPTHS OF PALM

430
00:20:51,451 --> 00:20:54,655
ON AN EXPEDITION TO
HELP OUR FRIENDS.

431
00:20:54,755 --> 00:20:57,924
WE FIGURED OUT A
WAY TO SHORTEN TRAVEL
TIME BETWEEN CITIES,

432
00:20:58,024 --> 00:21:00,293
SO YOU'RE NOT
ISOLATED ANYMORE.

433
00:21:00,393 --> 00:21:02,929
AND YOU NEED TO STOP
TERRORIZING PEOPLE.

434
00:21:03,029 --> 00:21:04,197
[ALL] UH...

435
00:21:04,297 --> 00:21:07,000
IT'S OBVIOUS WE'VE
WON THIS FIGHT.

436
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:08,168
IT'S UP TO YOU.

437
00:21:08,268 --> 00:21:11,137
WHAT'S IT GONNA BE, DEMICAS?

438
00:21:11,237 --> 00:21:13,707
[DEMICAS]
UGH. YOU LITTLE PUKE.

439
00:21:13,807 --> 00:21:15,709
I'M GONNA SEND ALL YOUR
SORRY ASSES THROUGH

440
00:21:15,809 --> 00:21:20,747
THE CATHEDRALS ONE
TIME AFTER ANOTHER!

441
00:21:20,847 --> 00:21:22,716
IT'S OVER FOR YOU!

442
00:21:22,816 --> 00:21:23,817
HA!

443
00:21:23,917 --> 00:21:25,151
STOP IT!

444
00:21:25,251 --> 00:21:26,853
AAH!

445
00:21:27,220 --> 00:21:29,355
AAH!

446
00:21:29,455 --> 00:21:31,057
[SERARA] HUH?

447
00:21:31,157 --> 00:21:35,395
[SHIROE] SEEMS LIKE
YOU'RE THE ONE TAKING
A TRIP TO THE CATHEDRAL.

448
00:21:35,495 --> 00:21:38,665
[DEMICAS] I WON'T
FORGET THIS, ENCHANTER!

449
00:21:38,765 --> 00:21:40,000
I'LL BE BACK!

450
00:21:40,100 --> 00:21:42,068
I'M COMING BACK FOR YOU!

451
00:21:42,168 --> 00:21:45,639
HA HA HA!

452
00:21:50,577 --> 00:21:53,013
[FLUTES BLOWING]
HUH?

453
00:21:55,048 --> 00:21:56,517
[RUSHING AIR]

454
00:21:57,718 --> 00:22:00,987
[NYAN‐TA] MY LADY,
YOUR RIDE AWAITS.

455
00:22:01,087 --> 00:22:02,589
[SERARA] HUH?

456
00:22:03,423 --> 00:22:04,090
[SHIROE] AKATSUKI.

457
00:22:04,190 --> 00:22:05,491
HUH?

458
00:22:06,226 --> 00:22:07,928
[SHIROE] LET'S MOVE OUT.

459
00:22:09,863 --> 00:22:11,598
HMM.

460
00:22:11,698 --> 00:22:13,734
MM‐HMM.

461
00:22:13,834 --> 00:22:17,237
LET'S GO, GUYS,
BACK TO AKIHABARA!

462
00:22:17,337 --> 00:22:20,741
LAST ONE THERE HAS
TO WASH MY CODPIECE!

463
00:22:22,876 --> 00:22:26,146
OH, MY GOD, OH, MY GOD,
OH, MY GOD, OH, MY GOD!

464
00:22:26,246 --> 00:22:27,147
[AKATSUKI]
MY LORD...

465
00:22:27,247 --> 00:22:30,083
WHAT CAN I
DO FOR YOU?

466
00:22:30,183 --> 00:22:32,519
HMM.

467
00:22:33,153 --> 00:22:34,788
OH, IT'S NOTHING.

468
00:22:34,888 --> 00:22:39,926
RIGHT. LET'S GO
HOME TO AKIHABARA.

469
00:22:40,460 --> 00:22:42,128
[AKATSUKI] YEAH.

470
00:24:14,888 --> 00:24:16,857
[AKATSUKI, VOICE‐OVER]
ON THEIR WAY BACK
TO AKIHABARA,

471
00:24:16,957 --> 00:24:19,760
