A MOMENT OF PEACE.

472
00:24:19,860 --> 00:24:22,395
AND THEN NYAN‐TA
REVEALS A SHOCKING TRUTH,

473
00:24:22,495 --> 00:24:26,767
A SECRET ABOUT THIS WORLD
THAT WILL CHANGE EVERYTHING
THEY THOUGHT THEY KNEW.

474
00:24:26,867 --> 00:24:28,835
MEANWHILE, YOUNG CHILDREN
IN THE CITY ARE SPENDING

475
00:24:28,935 --> 00:24:32,806
THEIR DAYS BEING EXPLOITED
WITH NO WAY OUT.

476
00:24:32,906 --> 00:24:36,042
[SHIROE]
THIS IS OUR REALITY.

